A massive industrial machine with countless interlocking gears, pistons, and cogs frozen in rust and decay, rendered in a vintage steampunk illustration style with sepia and copper tones. At the center, a small vibrant bird with iridescent feathers struggles to fly, its wings caught between two giant corroded gear teeth. Cobwebs stretch between motionless mechanical parts while small green sprouts attempt to push through cracks in the metal, only to be crushed by heavy brass weights suspended above them. The composition shows the oppressive scale of the bureaucratic machine towering over the trapped creative spirit, with dramatic shadows and Victorian-era technical drawing aesthetics, cross-hatching details, and aged paper texture throughout.
